---
title: Easy Creamy Salmon & Tomato Spaghetti with Pear & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Twirl your fork into a plate of pure bliss with this spaghetti spectacular! Perfectly cooked pasta meets tender, flaked salmon in a rich, tomato-infused cream sauce that’s downright irresistible. Paired with a crisp pear salad for a burst of freshness, this dish is a delicious balance of indulgence and zest. Dinner just got a whole lot more exciting!
